# --- MarNarMon (public, Apache-2.0) ---
# The dashboard source lives in dashboard/ and IS part of this repo. Its build
# artifacts (node_modules/, dist/) are ignored via dashboard/.gitignore.

# Agent/Cowork memory must never be committed (it lives outside the repo, but
# guard against an accidental copy/export into the project).
MEMORY.md
memory/
.claude/memory/
**/memory/

# Assistant working context — kept locally so Claude Code auto-loads it, but
# never committed to this public repo (a fork should not inherit our CLAUDE.md).
# The files stay on disk; they are untracked, not deleted.
CLAUDE.md
**/CLAUDE.md
# One-off internal handoff/spec artifacts must not land in the tree either.
DOCKER_MONITOR_SPEC.md
**/DOCKER_MONITOR_SPEC.md

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.venv/
venv/
*.egg-info/

# Local runtime artifacts
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
*.log

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
*.swp
dashboard/docker-compose.cfns.yml
